# Common Interview Questions

## Q1. Why denormalize data?

To improve query performance and reduce joins.

## Q2. Does denormalization violate best practice?

Not necessarily. Depends on workload.

## Q3. Where would you use it?

Warehouses, dashboards, reporting marts.

## Q4. Why not use in OLTP?

Updates become harder and consistency risk increases.

